      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SASSY SCARLETT (1) finds it hard to break through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when third (28.29) at this track. Has never been out of the money in four starts this course and distance. Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to be in the finish again. SUNSET GODDESS (5) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 488m behind Just A Sapphire (28.67) in a Novice race. Was a winner prior to that. Won at her only start from this draw. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SOUL SURFER (2) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at Cannington over 520m behind Sunset Clarice (30.71) in a Novice race. Leading chance. ELECTRIC KUNA (3) is worth a look despite no experience at this circuit.",
